title: Nominations for upcoming months presidential elections are being submitted
view-if: year = 1982 and month = 9 and week = 3
max-visits: 1
tags: event

Nominations are now being filled as candidates and their party faculty flood to the Election Commission building at Rajagiriya, Colombo.

News starts coming back as to who has correctly filed their candidacy.

- @unp: The UNP

